milestones.description: Graham Gooch and Bill Athey's 193-run partnership is the highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 188 between Ravi Shastri and Srikkanth
Graham Gooch and Bill Athey's 193-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 161 between Dennis Amiss and Mike Brearley
Martin Crowe and Jeff Crowe's 113-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 85 between Jeremy Coney and Bruce Blair
